"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"I recall when my partner Brad and I were raising our first USV fund, back in 2003, and potential investors wondered about my blogging habit. They asked if I was making a mistake telegraphing our investment thesis for everyone to see, including our “competitors.”\\n\\nWe strongly defended the practice and explained that the benefits of telling the world what we were looking to invest in, and why, strongly outweighed any costs. We explained that telegraphing would bring entrepreneurs to us.\\n\\nAnd that turned out to be the case. So many of our top-performing investments over the years came to us because of our telegraphing strategy. It is hard to know who is working on a problem you are interested in. But if you put the word out far and wide, they will find you.\\n\\nI was reminded of those conversations almost twenty years ago now when I read [this post on USV.com](https://www.usv.com/writing/2021/08/measurement-in-market-making/) by Hanel outlining [our interest in measuring carbon](https://www.usv.com/writing/2021/08/measurement-in-market-making/). She explains that we have made one investment in that area already and are looking to make more. And she explains why.\\n\\nI am sure that Hanel has already heard from a bunch of founders working on measuring carbon and will hear from more in the coming weeks and months. That’s excellent and how it should work in our view.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1629200373,\"title\":\"Telegraphing\",\"publication\":\"avc\"},\"digest\":\"Wu9W6_DwWZY2zExHMkmJqxt6mCh4GYlJJyh1q5So1l4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xB8332710AB60A1B2e8FE6D775d83524C9E0cE136\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FiD2ALymcePeEtTW-G9rQSmcPd1h4mDPeNiqNj5OjGw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"or7Oz7LuQf0j9f0zl2APv4Ys6kh8mj7L66G41AeIimw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"M895tcsrjlUUj1VKuAkjNtEIt2cQOYVmY7ifTOOo5qNfFcExLdQXZFJUiUy0CE4e7jICKuObZixA1ZOylYASdQ\",\"signingKey